WEBVTT

00:45.254 --> 00:48.966
PERFECT CROWN

00:59.851 --> 01:01.060
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

01:01.061 --> 01:02.980
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

01:03.563 --> 01:05.357
- When did I ever ask--
- Stop that.

01:05.941 --> 01:08.610
You didn't see a doctor
after what happened, did you?

01:14.491 --> 01:17.202
Don't you think
I'd be quite the supportive wife?

01:32.384 --> 01:33.385
What are you doing?

01:36.597 --> 01:37.681
Stay still.

02:12.591 --> 02:13.759
I saw a camera.

02:15.927 --> 02:16.928
Oh.

02:21.308 --> 02:23.434
Is it still there?

02:34.154 --> 02:35.696
Should we try that again?

02:35.697 --> 02:37.824
I think we can give them a better angle.

02:40.243 --> 02:41.453
Maybe like…

02:42.621 --> 02:43.622
Mmm.

02:45.040 --> 02:46.708
Mmm.

02:48.168 --> 02:49.543
Mmm.

02:49.544 --> 02:50.628
Now.

02:50.629 --> 02:52.381
Come on.

02:55.717 --> 02:58.970
PERFECT CROWN

02:59.554 --> 03:01.473
EPISODE 4

03:02.474 --> 03:04.308
Did you see their kiss last night?

03:04.309 --> 03:06.018
They're totally in love.

03:06.019 --> 03:08.355
- It kept me up all night.
- So romantic.

03:12.025 --> 03:13.068
Let's just go.

03:15.320 --> 03:16.822
Announcing Grand Prince I-AN.

03:18.156 --> 03:19.616
:cue

03:34.464 --> 03:36.257
LOVE ACROSS SOCIAL DIVIDES

03:36.258 --> 03:38.342
LOVE DEFYING SOCIAL CLASS…

03:38.343 --> 03:39.928
…I-AN AND SEONG'S MIDNIGHT TRYST

03:40.595 --> 03:42.848
We can no longer delay
an official statement.

03:43.598 --> 03:45.434
This matter will cause public unrest.

03:45.934 --> 03:47.101
We should be cautious--

03:47.102 --> 03:48.645
Staying silent now

03:49.229 --> 03:50.730
would only make things worse.

03:53.024 --> 03:54.650
Are you hoping I deny it?

03:54.651 --> 03:56.652
Your honor is at stake here.

03:56.653 --> 03:57.904
A grand prince…

03:59.781 --> 04:02.284
may kiss a woman and then
dismiss it as a mere dalliance?

04:02.784 --> 04:05.536
Is this the honor
you wish for me to uphold?

04:05.537 --> 04:06.538
That maiden

04:07.581 --> 04:10.124
is a mere commoner of illegitimate birth.

04:19.342 --> 04:20.635
Make it public.

04:28.059 --> 04:31.146
As His Royal Highness stated,
this is a scandal by a grand prince.

04:31.772 --> 04:33.439
We must do damage control.

04:33.440 --> 04:34.816
"Damage control"?

04:35.400 --> 04:36.735
With that in mind,

04:37.736 --> 04:38.862
you should confirm it.

04:41.323 --> 04:42.656
However,

04:42.657 --> 04:45.786
you must state firmly
that there is no prospect of marriage.

04:46.703 --> 04:48.996
Say that your acquaintance
has only just begun,

04:48.997 --> 04:50.457
with no talk of marriage.

04:51.875 --> 04:54.460
That should minimize any uncertainty.

04:54.461 --> 04:55.669
Prime Minister Min.

04:55.670 --> 04:58.714
There's nothing unusual about a young pair
falling in and out of love.

04:58.715 --> 05:00.091
If we treat it lightly,

05:00.926 --> 05:02.301
it will remain that way.

05:05.722 --> 05:06.806
Let it be so.

05:06.807 --> 05:07.808
However…

05:10.268 --> 05:12.770
that maiden should move out
of your private residence.

05:12.771 --> 05:14.605
- Why?
- Your Royal Highness!

05:14.606 --> 05:18.442
Not only was she pelted with eggs
at her own home with private security,

05:18.443 --> 05:21.195
but she is also bearing the brunt
of every insult online.

05:21.196 --> 05:22.489
As if that were not enough,

05:23.198 --> 05:26.034
she was photographed behind the palace,
under palace security.

05:26.535 --> 05:29.162
If anything happens to her
because she was left alone,

05:30.080 --> 05:31.414
will you answer for it?

05:37.045 --> 05:38.380
We may end up parting ways,

05:39.881 --> 05:41.758
or she may become my future wife.

05:43.510 --> 05:45.386
Your Royal Highness, how could you…

05:45.387 --> 05:47.347
My residence is already home to many.

05:50.725 --> 05:52.644
Attendants who maintain the grounds.

05:54.104 --> 05:55.688
The Royal Guard for my safety.

05:56.773 --> 05:58.567
And there are even cats
that roam in my garden.

06:00.235 --> 06:02.195
The addition of my lady to that list…

06:04.823 --> 06:06.824
will have little effect.

06:10.871 --> 06:12.622
Where will Your Royal Highness reside?

06:14.207 --> 06:17.627
If Ms. Seong is permitted to stay
at your private residence for her safety,

06:18.128 --> 06:20.130
then you must stay at the palace.

06:20.755 --> 06:22.841
If rumors spread
that the palace is divided…

06:25.051 --> 06:26.428
over a single woman,

06:27.512 --> 06:28.763
it will be a grave matter.

06:36.396 --> 06:37.479
:cue

06:37.480 --> 06:40.024
OFFICIAL STATEMENT

06:40.025 --> 06:41.693
This was approved?

06:42.611 --> 06:44.779
Is this how you chose
to handle the matter?

06:45.488 --> 06:49.326
- You must compose yourself.
- How can I?

06:51.161 --> 06:54.039
Even if marriage is ruled out,

06:54.539 --> 06:57.584
once the palace acknowledges them,
that woman will gain status.

06:58.293 --> 07:00.544
Public interest is already at its peak.

07:00.545 --> 07:02.546
Should he dare to include her
in state matters--

07:02.547 --> 07:03.798
If you knew as much,

07:05.467 --> 07:07.093
you should have exercised restraint.

07:09.262 --> 07:12.139
Had you just left it alone,
the matter would've resolved itself.

07:12.140 --> 07:14.058
Criticism was already pouring in.

07:14.059 --> 07:17.186
"Failure to uphold the dignity
of his station and proper decorum."

07:17.187 --> 07:18.854
They had plenty of grounds.

07:18.855 --> 07:20.065
However,

07:21.066 --> 07:24.027
because Your Majesty has opposed
the Grand Prince,

07:24.778 --> 07:27.071
public opinion has shifted in his favor.

07:27.072 --> 07:30.992
In fact, criticism of Your Majesty
has already begun to surface.

07:34.829 --> 07:36.122
Just give your approval.

07:38.750 --> 07:41.252
I will take care of the rest.

07:42.253 --> 07:44.547
Do you have a plan?

07:46.633 --> 07:50.344
There is no shortage of noblemen eager
to become the Prince's father-in-law,

07:50.345 --> 07:54.099
and plenty in the business world are eager
to keep that woman in check as well.

07:57.811 --> 07:59.729
That is to say,

08:00.605 --> 08:03.108
should something happen,
it would hardly be a surprise.

08:07.612 --> 08:10.739
The Royal Secretariat
has just released an official statement.

08:10.740 --> 08:13.450
In a royal first, the palace
has acknowledged a courtship

08:13.451 --> 08:15.202
that isn't an engagement or marriage.

08:15.203 --> 08:19.123
We'll discuss this with formal royal
spokesman, Professor Hwang Wookyeong.

08:19.124 --> 08:21.917
- Welcome.
- Hello, it's nice to meet you.

08:21.918 --> 08:24.920
You have always maintained the stance…

08:24.921 --> 08:26.004
Hwang Wookyeong?

08:26.005 --> 08:27.715
Don't you know who that is?

08:27.716 --> 08:31.260
He used to be a royal spokesman
before he got blacklisted.

08:31.261 --> 08:34.013
Come on, you must know him. Last year,

08:35.390 --> 08:36.932
he was the one who claimed

08:36.933 --> 08:39.935
the late king's death
wasn't an accident, but a murder.

08:39.936 --> 08:41.812
A nut who jumps to conspiracy theories.

08:41.813 --> 08:42.980
Be quiet.

08:42.981 --> 08:47.151
Many have noted that
this official statement is unprecedented.

08:47.152 --> 08:48.235
What do you think?

08:48.236 --> 08:51.071
I consider it to be
very befitting of the royal family.

08:51.072 --> 08:54.825
Castle Group's Seong Huiju
is a commoner and businesswoman.

08:54.826 --> 08:57.786
She is far from a traditional royal bride
by palace standards.

08:57.787 --> 09:00.914
But it would've been difficult
for the palace to deny the relationship.

09:00.915 --> 09:04.919
After all, there were
several definitive eyewitness accounts.

09:05.628 --> 09:07.629
So are you suggesting that

09:07.630 --> 09:09.757
they had no choice but to recognize it?

09:09.758 --> 09:11.967
-  That's correct.
-  Then Grand Prince I-AN…

09:11.968 --> 09:13.052
Seong Huiju.

09:13.053 --> 09:16.096
…and what is the likelihood of marriage?

09:16.097 --> 09:18.015
Marriage would be highly unlikely.

09:18.016 --> 09:20.769
Uh, I doubt the royal family
would accept a commoner,

09:21.686 --> 09:24.229
given their sensitivity about lineage.

09:24.230 --> 09:27.776
Then how do you think
the royal family will proceed?

09:28.318 --> 09:31.862
I don't expect them to provide
any further comments on the matter.

09:33.198 --> 09:34.865
THE GRAND PRINCE CLIMBED
OVER A WALL

09:34.866 --> 09:36.993
I knew this would happen.

09:37.744 --> 09:39.871
I told you we should've tried again.

09:41.039 --> 09:42.498
Well, I just…

09:42.499 --> 09:46.126
This angle is totally off. Darn it.

09:46.127 --> 09:47.836
What, are we in elementary school?

09:47.837 --> 09:50.255
We look like toddlers smooching.

09:50.256 --> 09:52.216
That's what you care about right now?

09:52.217 --> 09:53.885
- We kissed and--
- Your Royal Highness.

09:54.385 --> 09:55.803
Marketing only works

09:55.804 --> 09:59.807
when it's unbelievably sexy or shameless.

09:59.808 --> 10:00.933
"Courtship"?

10:00.934 --> 10:03.936
Wishy-washy words like that
will get us nowhere.

10:03.937 --> 10:05.313
A tryst at a hotel!
:cue

10:05.814 --> 10:07.356
That's sexy.

10:07.357 --> 10:09.150
Prince I-AN's shotgun wedding!

10:10.360 --> 10:12.611
That's shameless, right?

10:12.612 --> 10:16.157
Doesn't it sound tempting, like junk food?

10:40.598 --> 10:43.809
The quicker we get married,
the quicker we get divorced.

10:43.810 --> 10:45.812
Okay?

10:52.819 --> 10:55.946
Royal weddings are meant
to be conducted step by step…

10:55.947 --> 10:57.865
Do you have that much time to waste?

10:57.866 --> 10:59.074
I don't.

10:59.075 --> 11:00.325
I mean…

11:00.326 --> 11:03.370
Then what? Should we really make it
a shotgun wedding?

11:03.371 --> 11:05.497
- So it's sexy and shameless?
- Yes.

11:05.498 --> 11:08.376
When you pursue
a venture everyone opposes,

11:09.752 --> 11:12.338
you can't give them time to object.

11:12.922 --> 11:14.257
With that in mind…

11:16.634 --> 11:18.052
Are you free now?

11:21.890 --> 11:24.309
All of a sudden? Why do you ask?

11:30.440 --> 11:31.691
I have a little time.

11:34.277 --> 11:35.820
Can I take you somewhere?

11:37.405 --> 11:38.740
Let's speed things up a bit.

11:42.327 --> 11:43.328
Speed things up?

11:46.956 --> 11:47.999
That's enough.

11:48.625 --> 11:51.294
Do I look like a kindergartner to you?

11:52.212 --> 11:54.588
Stay still.

11:54.589 --> 11:56.924
Let's show them
what we're made of this time.

11:56.925 --> 12:00.762
Since when do people
show others up with their hair?

12:02.180 --> 12:05.600
You were in sweats in those photos
where you were caught sucking face.

12:06.100 --> 12:09.811
They must be roasting His
Royal Highness for having terrible taste.

12:09.812 --> 12:11.271
It makes me so upset.

12:11.272 --> 12:13.065
What's wrong with his taste?

12:13.066 --> 12:16.735
I mean, he chose me.
He clearly has exquisite taste.

12:16.736 --> 12:19.696
And those sweats are super expensive.

12:19.697 --> 12:23.283
Gosh. You must be a bird lover.

12:23.284 --> 12:25.828
Just look at that magnificent bird's nest
on your head.

12:28.498 --> 12:31.584
-  You did that on purpose. You…
- Stay still.

12:35.129 --> 12:38.007
You really want me to clear your day?
All of it?

12:41.302 --> 12:44.764
I'm just worried for your sake.
It'll make tomorrow brutal for you.

12:45.348 --> 12:46.598
And for me too.

12:46.599 --> 12:48.643
She wants to be Princess Diana.
What can I do?

12:49.269 --> 12:50.435
Princess Diana?

12:50.436 --> 12:53.689
As in Princess Diana from the UK?

12:53.690 --> 12:54.691
Jeez.

12:55.191 --> 12:58.277
All this fuss will die down with time.

12:58.278 --> 13:01.281
That's what the Queen Mother
is waiting for.

13:02.949 --> 13:04.367
I won't let that happen.

13:06.953 --> 13:08.121
Your Royal Highness.

13:18.089 --> 13:19.257
:cue

13:46.242 --> 13:47.367
Ta-da.

13:47.368 --> 13:49.829
Isn't she stunning?
Like an angel come to life.

13:53.958 --> 13:55.584
Sure…

13:55.585 --> 13:57.045
…ly not.

13:57.670 --> 14:00.214
You went for "spoiled princess"
and not an actual princess?

14:06.220 --> 14:07.888
Is he for real?

14:11.601 --> 14:13.686
I told you this wasn't my vibe!

14:23.029 --> 14:24.030
I mean,

14:24.822 --> 14:27.324
he's dressed in a princely suit.
What's his problem?

14:27.325 --> 14:29.367
That's what I'm saying, bro.

14:29.368 --> 14:30.495
He is beyond difficult.

14:36.501 --> 14:37.710
My goodness.

15:00.399 --> 15:01.775
Please give us a moment.

15:01.776 --> 15:03.402
- I shall quickly fix this--
- No need.

15:29.554 --> 15:30.763
Sorry about that.

15:50.950 --> 15:52.660
Thank you so much.

15:59.000 --> 16:02.919
Perhaps a bit too plain?

16:02.920 --> 16:04.172
Really?

16:05.047 --> 16:06.423
Hmm.

16:06.424 --> 16:08.092
I see what you mean.

16:08.718 --> 16:12.429
He does look a bit dull and old-fashioned.

16:15.558 --> 16:16.684
What the…

16:17.977 --> 16:19.436
- What are you doing?
-  Seriously?

16:19.437 --> 16:20.897
Are you feeling shy or something?

16:22.190 --> 16:23.940
A royal never feels shy… Oh.

16:23.941 --> 16:25.358
Just lose this.

16:25.359 --> 16:28.321
Losing the pocket square
makes it a little bit less dull.

16:29.071 --> 16:30.197
Better, right?

16:30.198 --> 16:33.951
No, I was actually talking
about you, Ms. Seong.

16:34.452 --> 16:35.785
Oh.

16:35.786 --> 16:36.871
Me?

16:37.455 --> 16:38.705
That's not possible.

16:38.706 --> 16:40.458
How could you ever call me plain?

16:46.297 --> 16:47.340
I'm dazzling.

16:52.261 --> 16:53.596
So pretty.

16:57.099 --> 16:58.267
:cue

17:14.742 --> 17:17.410
Go, Castle!

17:17.411 --> 17:21.831
- Let's go, Sharks!
- Let's go, Sharks!

17:21.832 --> 17:24.292
- Come on, Sharks!
- Let's go!

17:29.340 --> 17:31.425
It's not too late to call the Royal Guard.

17:32.468 --> 17:34.095
We'd be better without them here.

17:37.932 --> 17:38.933
Your Royal Highness!

17:39.684 --> 17:40.685
Ooh!

17:41.185 --> 17:42.186
Here we go.

17:43.271 --> 17:44.813
Let's see here.

17:44.814 --> 17:46.190
CASTLE SHARKS' LUCKY CHARM

17:46.774 --> 17:49.484
Ooh, I have such a keen eye for detail.

17:49.485 --> 17:50.820
You're 2XL, right?

17:51.362 --> 17:53.321
If we wear matching outfits…

17:53.322 --> 17:55.782
- He cannot.
- Why not?

17:55.783 --> 18:00.620
His Royal Highness can't wear uniforms.
No expression of political views.

18:00.621 --> 18:02.998
This isn't politics. It's just sports.

18:02.999 --> 18:05.625
"A royal's private life
is never truly private,"

18:05.626 --> 18:06.877
is the palace's position.

18:11.215 --> 18:13.384
Matching outfits would create some buzz.

18:15.011 --> 18:18.388
- Then you can just wear it, Aide Choi.
- Really?

18:18.389 --> 18:21.516
- It's so much more fun to cheer in this!
- So excited!

18:22.727 --> 18:25.604
Your Royal Highness,
remember I have warm undertones?

18:25.605 --> 18:26.647
This is perfect for me.

18:27.231 --> 18:28.940
- Huh?
- You're not wearing this.

18:28.941 --> 18:30.401
- Why not?
- Hmm?

18:42.788 --> 18:43.914
Hey, you!

18:44.665 --> 18:46.709
Why have you been ignoring my calls?

18:47.418 --> 18:48.419
Why you little…

18:49.545 --> 18:50.546
Oh, His Royal Highness?

18:51.380 --> 18:52.922
Your Royal Highness.

18:52.923 --> 18:54.800
What brings you to such squalid grounds?

18:56.510 --> 18:58.178
Fried chicken?

18:58.179 --> 18:59.721
You're getting ahead of yourself.

18:59.722 --> 19:03.099
We don't speak until His Royal Highness
speaks to us first.

19:03.100 --> 19:04.226
Oh!

19:04.894 --> 19:06.687
Huiju has told me a lot about you.

19:07.271 --> 19:08.355
About me?

19:08.356 --> 19:09.439
What?

19:09.440 --> 19:11.942
You better keep your trap shut.

19:12.652 --> 19:14.612
I wonder what she told you.

19:15.905 --> 19:17.073
Oh, right.

19:18.532 --> 19:19.659
Yes.

19:21.952 --> 19:25.205
It is an honor to make your acquaintance,
Your Royal Highness.

19:25.206 --> 19:26.916
I am Dayeong of the Han Family.

19:27.541 --> 19:28.667
And your father's name?

19:28.668 --> 19:31.420
He is Jeongseok of the Han family.

19:32.129 --> 19:33.631
Former Minister of Justice.

19:34.799 --> 19:36.342
What a commendable father you have.

19:41.889 --> 19:42.890
Oh.

19:44.266 --> 19:46.059
Jeongwoo's throwing the first pitch?

19:46.060 --> 19:47.686
All right. Let's go!

19:50.773 --> 19:54.192
It appears we have Prime
Minister Min for the first pitch today.

19:54.193 --> 19:55.276
That's right.

19:55.277 --> 19:57.404
He's famous for being
a hardcore fan of the Castle Sharks.

19:57.405 --> 20:02.033
I hear he even dreamed of being
a baseball player when he was young.

20:02.034 --> 20:04.370
I'm excited to see
how his first pitch will turn out.

20:11.669 --> 20:14.671
That was
a beautiful pitch. Do you hear that crowd?

20:14.672 --> 20:16.840
The crowd is going wild for him.

20:16.841 --> 20:18.925
The crowd's love for Prime Minister Min is

20:18.926 --> 20:21.261
through the roof here
at Gocheok Sky Dome today.

20:21.262 --> 20:22.512
I couldn't agree more.

20:24.682 --> 20:26.058
Min Jeongwoo!

20:33.774 --> 20:35.151
Up to bat is Gang Suho.

20:36.610 --> 20:38.945
He pulled that one. It's high and deep.

20:38.946 --> 20:40.196
Is it going over?

20:40.197 --> 20:41.614
Over the wall and gone!

20:41.615 --> 20:44.075
Gang Suho pulls off a comeback win!

20:44.076 --> 20:45.786
Home run!
:cue

20:46.746 --> 20:47.830
Nanny Jung!

20:48.456 --> 20:49.581
You okay?

20:49.582 --> 20:52.083
The Castle Sharks
are sinking their teeth in…

20:52.084 --> 20:53.252
Are you all right?

20:55.045 --> 20:57.173
I am fine, Your Majesty.

20:58.299 --> 21:00.301
But the treat from Lord INPYEONG is…

21:01.093 --> 21:02.511
No need for concern.

21:06.307 --> 21:08.309
The corndog is safe.

21:09.518 --> 21:11.353
It certainly is not, Your Majesty!

21:11.854 --> 21:13.646
If we take a look, the stands are packed

21:13.647 --> 21:15.149
with fans in Castle Sharks jerseys…

21:17.443 --> 21:19.987
Your Royal Highness.

21:20.571 --> 21:22.155
- The Sharks…
- Stop it, babe.

21:22.156 --> 21:24.657
Get lost.

21:24.658 --> 21:26.785
Let's go, Gang Suho!

21:26.786 --> 21:28.829
You got this, Sharks!

21:30.623 --> 21:31.624
Your Royal Highness.

21:32.208 --> 21:33.209
Jeongwoo.

21:34.001 --> 21:36.962
You didn't leave after the first pitch?
I thought you'd already left.

21:37.546 --> 21:39.506
My secretary said
not to waste the photo op.

21:39.507 --> 21:41.174
Photo op?

21:49.141 --> 21:51.560
Scooch over, Your Royal Highness.
Jeongwoo needs a seat.

21:55.397 --> 21:56.398
Scooch over.

21:59.360 --> 22:00.528
Come sit here, Jeongwoo.

22:05.991 --> 22:07.201
You should have some too.

22:08.035 --> 22:09.202
No, thank you.

22:09.203 --> 22:10.204
You're not hungry?

22:11.288 --> 22:12.873
- I am.
- Then eat.

22:14.041 --> 22:16.001
Are you a picky eater?

22:17.211 --> 22:19.839
- It's not that…
- He can only eat at restaurants.

22:20.422 --> 22:21.631
Why?

22:21.632 --> 22:24.093
Because quality and safety
can't be guaranteed elsewhere.

22:24.593 --> 22:25.678
And it's quite unseemly.

22:28.180 --> 22:29.515
Am I expected to do that too?

22:30.015 --> 22:33.393
-  Kiss!
-  Kiss!

22:33.394 --> 22:36.855
- Kiss!
- Kiss!

22:36.856 --> 22:40.358
On the Kiss Cam,
we have the hottest couple of the moment.

22:40.359 --> 22:41.734
-  That's right.
- It's them.

22:41.735 --> 22:42.819
Oh, my gosh!

22:42.820 --> 22:44.654
They really look great together.

22:44.655 --> 22:47.365
But I'm sure it won't be easy
for His Royal Highness to kiss

22:47.366 --> 22:48.741
- on the Kiss Cam.
- Right.

22:48.742 --> 22:50.743
- Kiss!
- No! Stop!

22:50.744 --> 22:53.371
- Kiss!
- No! They can't kiss!

22:53.372 --> 22:57.500
- Kiss!
- No kiss! Where's the camera?

22:57.501 --> 23:00.461
- Kiss!
- Kiss!

23:00.462 --> 23:03.756
- Kiss!
- No! They can't kiss! No kiss!

23:03.757 --> 23:05.300
No kiss!

23:05.301 --> 23:17.562
- Kiss!
- Kiss!

23:17.563 --> 23:18.813
MUST UPHOLD HIS DECORUM

23:22.401 --> 23:23.402
Sorry, we can't.

23:23.903 --> 23:24.904
No, we can't!

23:25.446 --> 23:26.530
We can't kiss.

23:39.084 --> 23:40.085
Hold on.

23:40.669 --> 23:44.047
How are we supposed to be photographed
if they're covering us like this?

23:45.799 --> 23:47.926
- Huiju, let's go get dinner.
- Yeah?

23:47.927 --> 23:49.136
We had corndogs already.

23:49.720 --> 23:51.180
That's not enough to fill you up.

23:51.722 --> 23:53.265
Remember what you wanted last time?

23:54.016 --> 23:55.601
- Last time?
- Yeah.

23:56.518 --> 23:59.145
Mmm. Oh, that!

24:00.230 --> 24:01.231
Your Royal Highness.

24:02.274 --> 24:03.358
Yes?

24:03.359 --> 24:04.360
Back to the palace?

24:05.319 --> 24:07.111
- What?
- Go on without me.

24:07.112 --> 24:08.696
I'll have dinner with Jeongwoo.

24:08.697 --> 24:09.990
I shall join you.

24:10.699 --> 24:11.783
Pardon?

24:11.784 --> 24:15.162
We came here together, so wouldn't it
be odd if we left separately?

24:16.121 --> 24:17.122
Hmm.

24:26.006 --> 24:27.007
Mmm.
:cue

24:36.016 --> 24:37.726
Bye!

24:55.911 --> 24:56.996
Prime Minister Min.

24:57.663 --> 24:58.831
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

25:00.499 --> 25:01.792
Slow day at the office?

25:03.460 --> 25:04.545
Pardon?

25:16.015 --> 25:17.558
Mmm, it looks so good.

25:18.809 --> 25:19.893
Please eat up.

25:24.898 --> 25:27.276
We can't eat before you take a bite.
Please, go ahead.

25:28.485 --> 25:30.278
You should've gone back to the palace.

25:30.279 --> 25:33.115
Hmm? What now? Is there another issue?

25:33.615 --> 25:35.367
This is a restaurant, isn't it?

25:35.909 --> 25:37.076
I know.

25:37.077 --> 25:38.953
A royal shall never consume raw food.

25:38.954 --> 25:39.955
It's the law.

25:41.123 --> 25:43.917
Shall we order some gyeran-jjim
or doenjang soup for you?

25:44.501 --> 25:45.793
- No need.
- Wait, hold on.

25:45.794 --> 25:47.962
So, raw food? Nothing raw?

25:47.963 --> 25:50.798
Not even beef tartare?
You can't have anything like that?

25:50.799 --> 25:52.968
I cannot.
The risk of food poisoning is too high.

25:54.636 --> 25:55.763
What a load of crap.

25:56.555 --> 25:57.556
Load of…

25:59.767 --> 26:02.560
-  A load of crap…
- You can't have street food.

26:02.561 --> 26:04.145
Nothing raw either.

26:04.146 --> 26:06.440
Where are you supposed
to find the joy in life?

26:07.232 --> 26:09.567
That's why you shouldn't marry
His Royal Highness.

26:09.568 --> 26:10.652
Too many restrictions.

26:11.945 --> 26:14.281
What else? What else can't you do?

26:25.834 --> 26:27.252
Here I am.

26:30.631 --> 26:31.923
Should we do this puzzle?

26:31.924 --> 26:35.218
Hwan, may I try on your Dragon Robe?

26:35.219 --> 26:36.220
Sure.

26:41.100 --> 26:42.101
Let's see here.

26:43.727 --> 26:46.020
Whoa, you look great in it.

26:46.021 --> 26:48.482
- It looks good on me, right?
- Yeah.

26:49.733 --> 26:52.653
Father, Hwan said I could…

26:56.406 --> 26:58.117
How dare you mock

26:58.700 --> 27:01.161
the Crown Prince's authority!

27:13.590 --> 27:15.925
Do not wear red.

27:15.926 --> 27:17.261
That is the king's color.

27:18.220 --> 27:19.637
Do not walk ahead.

27:21.223 --> 27:22.683
The king always leads.

27:25.561 --> 27:27.896
Do not question anything.

27:29.731 --> 27:31.316
It is the king's command.

27:58.427 --> 27:59.720
Eat up while you still can.

28:00.971 --> 28:04.141
You won't be able to
after the royal wedding.

28:08.937 --> 28:09.938
Mmm.

28:15.652 --> 28:18.447
Mmm, so good. It's delicious.
:cue

28:21.116 --> 28:22.408
Your Royal Highness.

28:22.409 --> 28:24.161
Were you at a raw fish restaurant?

28:24.661 --> 28:27.288
- Do not worry. I did not eat any.
- And a baseball stadium?

28:27.289 --> 28:28.873
Do not worry about that either.

28:28.874 --> 28:30.207
No personal show of support.

28:30.208 --> 28:31.542
No security issues.

28:31.543 --> 28:33.253
It was unannounced, so no reporters.

28:33.837 --> 28:35.838
You should have maintained decorum.

28:35.839 --> 28:37.256
I did.

28:37.257 --> 28:40.092
What is the use if you maintain it,
when she will not?

28:40.093 --> 28:41.803
Because she has no reason to.

28:42.679 --> 28:44.722
She is not a member
of the royal family yet.

28:45.807 --> 28:50.062
Do you truly not see that her faults
will soon become your own?

28:51.897 --> 28:54.358
What on earth were you doing
while this unfolded?

28:58.528 --> 28:59.821
We have no other choice.

29:00.322 --> 29:01.573
I shall step in.

29:02.491 --> 29:03.574
And do what?

29:03.575 --> 29:07.078
Your Royal Highness cannot be
expected to know a woman's proprieties,

29:07.079 --> 29:10.707
and it would be improper
for the Queen Mother to step forward.

29:11.375 --> 29:12.918
That leaves only me, does it not?

29:13.669 --> 29:17.380
I… am afraid I do not understand.

29:17.381 --> 29:18.382
Please allow me

29:19.508 --> 29:21.176
to discipline her.

29:27.557 --> 29:30.142
Even palace attendants
who run wild like colts

29:30.143 --> 29:31.478
become well-behaved

29:32.062 --> 29:33.730
after I am done with them.

29:34.439 --> 29:36.024
Rest assured, Your Royal Highness.

29:39.820 --> 29:40.821
Goodness me.

29:42.948 --> 29:45.199
Such excellent news. I am so relieved.

29:45.200 --> 29:47.910
I have full faith in you.

29:47.911 --> 29:49.870
Such excellent news indeed.

29:56.628 --> 29:59.588
Gosh, are you leaving already?
You need to have breakfast.

29:59.589 --> 30:01.507
It's okay. I normally skip breakfast.

30:01.508 --> 30:03.175
That simply will not do. Eat up.

30:03.176 --> 30:05.595
Special apple bunnies for you. Open up.

30:06.346 --> 30:07.472
There's some fuzz here.

30:08.056 --> 30:09.307
- It's okay.
- Open up.

30:12.686 --> 30:14.603
We can skip all this next time--

30:14.604 --> 30:16.356
- Have a lovely day.
- Have a lovely day.

30:17.774 --> 30:18.775
Hmm.

30:20.110 --> 30:21.111
Mmm.

30:51.725 --> 30:53.726
Oh, right. We met at the palace last time.

30:53.727 --> 30:55.853
I am Jinsook of the Choi Family.

30:55.854 --> 30:58.106
Feel free to address me
as Court Lady Choi.

30:58.690 --> 30:59.816
Court Lady Choi.

31:00.525 --> 31:01.777
Where are my manners?

31:04.988 --> 31:05.989
I am Seong Huiju.

31:06.990 --> 31:09.033
I am the head court lady
of Anhwadang Hall,

31:09.034 --> 31:10.535
the residence of the Grand Prince…

31:17.125 --> 31:18.335
Hey, Ms. Do.

31:20.128 --> 31:22.964
Of course, I'm on my way.

31:24.883 --> 31:26.551
Yes, I swear I'm on my way.

31:27.052 --> 31:29.805
I can see Umyeonsan Tunnel up ahead.

31:32.265 --> 31:33.891
I'm almost there.

31:33.892 --> 31:35.644
I see you, Ms. Do.

31:36.144 --> 31:37.437
I'm not lying!

31:38.563 --> 31:39.606
So?

31:40.148 --> 31:41.941
You just got in the car and left?

31:41.942 --> 31:44.236
Yes. Was it something urgent?

31:45.862 --> 31:47.906
Court Lady Choi must be irritated.

31:49.449 --> 31:50.742
Why?

31:53.954 --> 31:56.623
She has been biding her time to teach you.

31:58.625 --> 32:00.334
What exactly would she teach me?

32:00.335 --> 32:04.255
The overall protocols, history,
and hierarchy of the royal family.

32:04.256 --> 32:05.465
Things like that.

32:13.932 --> 32:15.058
Good morning, Ms…

32:15.934 --> 32:17.811
That sounds like a waste of time.

32:19.020 --> 32:20.981
Fine. I'll take the lessons.

32:21.523 --> 32:23.108
I need to go. Bye.

32:29.865 --> 32:30.866
Wow.

32:32.951 --> 32:35.704
Are you sure
you two weren't close in school?

32:38.206 --> 32:39.541
What? Why?

32:40.041 --> 32:41.209
It's just that

32:41.751 --> 32:43.587
you two make such a cute couple.

32:52.971 --> 32:53.972
Cute couple, my foot.

32:56.808 --> 32:59.227
What? There's a lot to do today.

32:59.853 --> 33:01.395
You have a lot of meetings too.
:cue

33:01.396 --> 33:03.022
You couldn't trim it down a bit?

33:03.023 --> 33:04.899
I did. I trimmed a lot.

33:05.984 --> 33:08.235
Fine, let's hear it. Keep it very brief.

33:08.236 --> 33:12.114
First off, you have a new product testing
with the R&D manager in one hour.

33:12.115 --> 33:13.657
You have one hour to do that.

33:13.658 --> 33:14.659
One hour?

33:15.160 --> 33:16.786
- For a new product testing?
- Yes.

33:17.287 --> 33:20.414
You have lunch with Gang Taehyun
from Castle Pharma at 1:00.

33:22.042 --> 33:23.792
Why would he have lunch with me?

33:23.793 --> 33:25.085
Isn't he in Taeju's circle?

33:25.086 --> 33:26.795
He joined yours as of yesterday.

33:26.796 --> 33:29.131
All of a sudden?

33:29.132 --> 33:30.799
Didn't you also kiss the Grand Prince

33:30.800 --> 33:32.552
all of a sudden?

33:40.101 --> 33:41.227
Was he good?

33:41.228 --> 33:42.311
What?

33:42.312 --> 33:45.356
I mean, the cheeks were flushed.
Totally blushing for real.

33:45.357 --> 33:46.358
Hey, come on.

33:47.150 --> 33:49.902
I was really hot that night.

33:49.903 --> 33:51.863
That outfit is surprisingly warm.

33:53.573 --> 33:54.950
Not you.

33:55.617 --> 33:56.785
His Royal Highness.

33:57.619 --> 33:58.703
What?

33:59.371 --> 34:01.039
Did you get all fluttery too?

34:03.708 --> 34:04.751
Listen, Ms. Do.

34:05.252 --> 34:06.835
Do I look like a teenager to you?

34:06.836 --> 34:11.006
Why would I blush and get all fluttery
over a measly kiss?

34:11.007 --> 34:12.132
Don't make me laugh.

34:12.133 --> 34:14.552
I see. Not so great, huh?

34:15.053 --> 34:17.055
Then again, he has no dating experience.

34:19.182 --> 34:21.976
He has no dating experience?

34:21.977 --> 34:22.978
Really?

34:23.561 --> 34:26.147
He's never publicly dated anyone.
No tabloid rumors either.

34:26.731 --> 34:28.817
That's what you meant?

34:29.734 --> 34:31.068
You may be wrong about that.

34:31.069 --> 34:32.070
Hmm.

34:32.612 --> 34:34.280
I guess he was surprisingly good.

34:34.281 --> 34:35.907
Yeah, he clearly knew his way around…

34:36.616 --> 34:39.159
Hey. That's not what I meant!

34:41.204 --> 34:43.289
I'm not sure what you meant, but I got it.

34:43.290 --> 34:45.040
Shall we get going now?

34:45.041 --> 34:46.458
Why? What now?

34:46.459 --> 34:48.877
We'll barely have enough time
for the tailor as it is.

34:48.878 --> 34:50.337
New clothes?

34:50.338 --> 34:51.339
For what?

34:52.007 --> 34:53.090
Prime Minister Min did?

34:53.091 --> 34:54.342
That's what I'm telling you.

34:54.843 --> 34:55.885
It hasn't…

34:56.928 --> 34:58.846
Could we have some privacy?

34:58.847 --> 35:00.056
Yes, sir.

35:05.478 --> 35:07.563
It hasn't been made public yet,

35:07.564 --> 35:10.566
but the PR team said
he invited Huiju to the roundtable.

35:10.567 --> 35:12.693
But even Father was never invited to that.

35:12.694 --> 35:15.487
Exactly! He threw money
and sucked up to them for an invite,

35:15.488 --> 35:18.407
but they treated him like dirt
because he wasn't a noble.

35:19.534 --> 35:22.077
Why would they invite Seong Huiju?

35:22.078 --> 35:25.831
Babe, what would you hate more?
Huiju moving up in society

35:25.832 --> 35:27.667
or becoming the heir to Castle Group?

35:28.460 --> 35:29.627
I hate both equally.

35:29.628 --> 35:32.296
But still, out of the two,
wouldn't the former be better?

35:32.297 --> 35:36.467
Do you really want to see me bow down
and address her as Your Highness?

35:36.468 --> 35:39.219
Babe, you need to step back
and see the bigger picture.

35:39.220 --> 35:42.515
She doesn't become "Her Highness"
just because she marries him.

35:43.058 --> 35:45.351
We may have to bow down a bit…

35:46.436 --> 35:48.146
- Hey, Han Dayeong. I--
- But!

35:48.730 --> 35:50.105
She can't run a business.

35:50.106 --> 35:52.651
Royals aren't allowed
to engage in economic activities.

35:54.152 --> 35:55.527
No, I still don't like it.

35:55.528 --> 35:58.031
What if she divorces him
after she becomes "Her Highness"?

35:58.907 --> 36:00.240
Babe.

36:00.241 --> 36:01.993
Have you ever heard of a royal divorce?

36:04.162 --> 36:05.537
I thought they could.

36:05.538 --> 36:06.705
If that were true,

36:06.706 --> 36:09.541
Grand Prince I-AN
should've ascended the throne.

36:09.542 --> 36:11.586
Wouldn't that have made more sense?

36:13.004 --> 36:14.005
Maybe you're right.

36:14.714 --> 36:17.883
- Babe, we should get a gift for Huiju.
- What?

36:17.884 --> 36:20.636
We'll back her up
and get her married off to the Crown

36:20.637 --> 36:22.722
so you can claim
Castle Group all for yourself.

36:26.476 --> 36:28.520
I don't know.

36:31.147 --> 36:32.148
Come on now.

36:33.900 --> 36:35.151
Who does Taeju belong to?

36:35.819 --> 36:36.820
To Dayeong.

36:38.029 --> 36:39.948
Who does Castle Group belong to?

36:43.118 --> 36:44.201
To me.

37:04.013 --> 37:05.473
You stopped driving it around?

37:06.558 --> 37:08.851
- What?
- The red open-top car.

37:08.852 --> 37:10.019
Mmm.

37:10.562 --> 37:11.646
Huh?

37:12.188 --> 37:13.689
Did the Prince tell you to stop?

37:14.941 --> 37:16.901
As if I would ever listen.

37:18.153 --> 37:19.653
It's in the shop.

37:19.654 --> 37:21.489
They have a pick-up
and drop-off service now.

37:22.365 --> 37:23.491
It broke down?

37:24.033 --> 37:25.534
But you just got that car.

37:25.535 --> 37:28.537
Yeah. Someone hit the bumper and ran.

37:28.538 --> 37:29.621
Who?

37:29.622 --> 37:30.957
How would I know?

37:32.250 --> 37:33.251
But then again,

37:34.127 --> 37:36.629
there are a lot of people
who'd like to crash my car.
:cue

37:47.682 --> 37:49.392
I'm back.

37:51.352 --> 37:52.770
Her Ladyship is here.

37:52.771 --> 37:55.022
- Let me help you.
- Your Ladyship!

37:55.023 --> 37:56.899
- I'll take that.
- No, I can carry them.

37:56.900 --> 37:58.150
Just let me.

37:58.151 --> 38:00.611
- Did you go shopping?
- Yeah. I can put those away.

38:00.612 --> 38:01.780
Did you have dinner?

38:02.655 --> 38:04.114
I had a light salad.

38:04.115 --> 38:05.574
Get Her Ladyship dinner first.

38:05.575 --> 38:06.825
- No, it's okay.
- Sure.

38:06.826 --> 38:09.370
- We made sujeonggwa earlier--
- You are late.

38:25.470 --> 38:26.721
I know it is late,

38:27.347 --> 38:29.557
but your royal education
cannot be delayed.

38:30.642 --> 38:32.018
I ask for your understanding.

38:33.770 --> 38:35.646
Yes, of course.

38:35.647 --> 38:38.233
I understand.
I understand indeed.

38:40.026 --> 38:41.902
Do not repeat yourself.

38:41.903 --> 38:43.363
It makes you look frivolous.

38:44.322 --> 38:45.490
Okay.

38:46.658 --> 38:48.535
Dragging out the ends of your words

38:49.202 --> 38:50.286
is also forbidden.

38:51.830 --> 38:52.872
Yep.

38:53.748 --> 38:56.959
Your education will be comprehensive.

38:56.960 --> 39:01.505
For your public role, you will learn
royal protocol, royal history,

39:01.506 --> 39:04.342
proper conduct, and the court hierarchy.

39:04.843 --> 39:05.926
For your private role,

39:05.927 --> 39:08.846
you will learn who to meet
and whom to avoid.

39:08.847 --> 39:10.265
What to say…

39:11.975 --> 39:14.685
and what not to say.

39:14.686 --> 39:16.896
Let us start with your posture.

39:27.282 --> 39:29.075
Your standing posture

39:30.326 --> 39:31.452
is good.

39:32.745 --> 39:33.746
Please walk.

39:34.497 --> 39:35.498
Up to there.

39:36.374 --> 39:37.458
Mmm.

39:43.214 --> 39:44.424
More energy.

39:56.811 --> 39:57.854
Stand up straight.

40:01.983 --> 40:04.569
Can you not even stand still?

40:17.832 --> 40:19.417
Though you are small in stature,

40:19.918 --> 40:21.419
do not bow your head.

40:22.503 --> 40:24.504
Posture is dignity.

40:24.505 --> 40:26.090
Do you understand?

40:27.091 --> 40:29.552
Yes, Queen Mother.

40:33.181 --> 40:36.224
No, that is not right.

40:37.936 --> 40:39.728
Let me show you one last time.

40:39.729 --> 40:41.022
Watch carefully.

40:44.233 --> 40:46.485
Like this.

40:46.486 --> 40:49.279
Extend your leg.

40:49.280 --> 40:50.406
Extend…

40:50.990 --> 40:52.200
Oh, dear.

40:54.077 --> 40:55.452
Right here.

40:55.453 --> 40:57.996
- It hurts right here, doesn't it?
- Yes, it does.

40:57.997 --> 40:59.958
You have so many knots here.

41:00.541 --> 41:02.542
This must hurt a lot.

41:02.543 --> 41:04.086
- Yes, a bit.
- Here too.

41:04.087 --> 41:06.338
- Does this hurt even more?
- That is right.

41:06.339 --> 41:08.257
Oh, my goodness.

41:09.133 --> 41:12.219
I've been doing Pilates for ten years,

41:12.220 --> 41:14.722
so I can just tell from someone's posture.
:cue

41:15.598 --> 41:19.226
- Now is not the time for this…
- No, now is exactly the right time.

41:19.227 --> 41:20.936
Let's try that once more.

41:20.937 --> 41:22.604
- All right.
- I'll help you.

41:22.605 --> 41:25.774
- Like this?
- There you go. Lift your leg and…

41:25.775 --> 41:27.192
Good.

41:27.193 --> 41:28.528
You said to leave it to you.

41:29.278 --> 41:30.738
Is this how you discipline?

41:31.406 --> 41:32.615
Your Royal Highness!

41:57.432 --> 41:58.433
Hey.

41:59.308 --> 42:00.643
We have a lot of eyes on us.

42:01.728 --> 42:03.563
Please take her away.

42:04.772 --> 42:05.857
What?

42:06.774 --> 42:08.817
Do you know how much work I have to do?

42:08.818 --> 42:11.863
Must I devote my whole night
to posture correction?

42:14.574 --> 42:16.117
Your Royal Highness.

42:21.456 --> 42:23.750
What brings you to your private residence?

42:24.959 --> 42:26.878
I have been away from it for far too long.

42:27.545 --> 42:30.672
And I was curious to see
how your royal lessons were progressing.

42:30.673 --> 42:32.090
Please make your return.

42:32.091 --> 42:33.634
The palace gates will soon be shut.

42:41.225 --> 42:42.976
- You should come with me.
- Pardon?

42:42.977 --> 42:45.229
Your primary duty
is to protect Anhwadang Hall,

42:45.813 --> 42:47.356
not discipline her. Is that not so?

42:47.857 --> 42:50.025
- But Your Royal Highness--
- Do not argue.

42:50.026 --> 42:51.110
It is my command.

43:15.593 --> 43:17.220
With the Ancestral Rite concluded,

43:17.720 --> 43:19.680
we will begin planning the overseas tour.

43:26.145 --> 43:27.355
How many stops this year?

43:29.732 --> 43:31.359
It should be similar to last year.

43:36.072 --> 43:38.199
Why? Shall I reduce them?

43:38.783 --> 43:39.951
Won't you stop me?

43:42.078 --> 43:43.329
- What?
- My marriage.

43:44.539 --> 43:46.123
I thought you'd try at least once.

43:48.626 --> 43:49.669
I am not you.

44:02.473 --> 44:04.891
You may be able to decide something

44:04.892 --> 44:07.812
simply based on whether you find
something agreeable or not.

44:09.230 --> 44:10.565
But if I do that…

44:21.450 --> 44:22.910
the country would collapse.

44:23.494 --> 44:24.912
Checkmate.

44:28.457 --> 44:29.876
I'd rather you yelled at me.

44:36.257 --> 44:37.842
I handled the Junghwajeon incident.

44:40.344 --> 44:43.181
The Queen Mother should no longer
take issue with it either.
:cue

44:51.439 --> 44:53.191
In a royal funeral,

44:54.025 --> 44:57.987
the body is cleansed and an ablution
is performed at the Place of Passing,

44:58.696 --> 45:01.823
along with the ritual wailing,
the fencing, mouth-filling,

45:01.824 --> 45:03.909
and ice-bedding ceremonies.

45:03.910 --> 45:06.954
- The Royal Ancestral Altar--
- They really do all that?

45:08.164 --> 45:11.334
It is discourteous to interrupt.

45:11.918 --> 45:14.295
My apologies. I was just really curious.

45:14.921 --> 45:17.506
Did they do all that three years ago too?

45:18.174 --> 45:19.342
That is correct.

45:20.176 --> 45:21.594
Why don't I remember it at all?

45:23.095 --> 45:26.390
The last public funeral ceremony
held by the royal family

45:26.933 --> 45:28.726
was in 2005.

45:29.435 --> 45:30.436
Why?

45:32.688 --> 45:36.025
The mother of the Grand Prince,
Queen UIHYEON,

45:36.817 --> 45:38.985
passed away 20 years ago,

45:38.986 --> 45:41.572
in the fourth lunar month
of the Eulyu year.

45:48.037 --> 45:52.207
His father, King HUIJONG,
passed away seven years later,

45:52.208 --> 45:55.795
in the sixth month of the Imjin year.

46:06.722 --> 46:08.640
And just three years ago,

46:08.641 --> 46:10.559
His Majesty's father

46:11.143 --> 46:15.314
and Grand Prince I-AN's older brother,
King SEONJONG, passed away.

46:21.612 --> 46:23.364
With tragedies so frequent,

46:23.990 --> 46:26.616
the royal family decided
to keep the ceremony private.

46:30.246 --> 46:31.329
Your Ladyship?

46:31.330 --> 46:32.872
It's just all too much.

46:32.873 --> 46:34.959
- Pardon?
- It's no wonder

46:35.584 --> 46:38.087
His Royal Highness
has a chip on his shoulder.

46:38.587 --> 46:40.298
I mean, I knew all about it,

46:41.674 --> 46:43.592
but to hear about it one after the other…

46:48.222 --> 46:49.348
Don't mind me.

46:51.183 --> 46:52.977
I just want to be alone right now.

47:05.614 --> 47:07.032
QUEEN UIHYEON PASSED AWAY…

47:07.033 --> 47:08.326
"Queen UIHYEON

47:09.035 --> 47:11.245
passed away
in a vehicle rollover accident."

47:13.622 --> 47:14.748
KING HUIJONG PASSED…

47:14.749 --> 47:17.126
"King HUIJONG passed away
after a heart attack."

47:18.002 --> 47:19.879
"Could it have been prevented?"

47:23.966 --> 47:27.845
"King SEONJONG
tragically met his death in a fire."

47:38.105 --> 47:39.773
And if he suffers indigestion?

47:39.774 --> 47:41.149
You would be wholly to blame.

47:41.150 --> 47:42.777
And if Queen Mother is angered?

47:44.403 --> 47:46.530
Is that why he was so on edge back then?

47:55.373 --> 47:57.666
PRINCE

48:09.470 --> 48:10.513
Is he working?
:cue

48:19.605 --> 48:20.815
Please introduce yourself.

48:21.690 --> 48:24.360
She has been
my closest companion recently.

48:27.029 --> 48:29.031
I am Jaegyeong of the Kim Family,

48:29.532 --> 48:30.866
Your Royal Highness.

48:31.867 --> 48:35.538
There is a dinner
with the royal correspondents tomorrow.

48:36.705 --> 48:39.707
I cannot accompany you due to my illness.

48:39.708 --> 48:40.876
Take her in my stead.

48:42.002 --> 48:44.213
Her father is
the proprietor of Jeongui Daily.

48:44.797 --> 48:46.382
She will be able to aid you.

48:50.511 --> 48:53.847
You have been falling ill
quite frequently lately.

48:53.848 --> 48:56.434
Perhaps because I have had
a lot on my mind.

48:59.019 --> 49:00.187
Court Lady Im, approach.

49:02.773 --> 49:04.275
What is Her Majesty's ailment?

49:04.859 --> 49:05.860
Pardon?

49:06.819 --> 49:08.237
She has been ill for a few days.

49:08.863 --> 49:11.030
The royal physician must have visited.

49:11.031 --> 49:13.075
What is Her Majesty's ailment?

49:18.539 --> 49:20.166
You have failed in your duties.

49:20.708 --> 49:22.126
Not at all, Your Royal Highness.

49:24.420 --> 49:26.379
Instruct the royal physician

49:26.380 --> 49:29.383
to monitor Her Majesty's condition
three times a day.

49:29.967 --> 49:33.637
The illness may spread,
so private audiences must be forbidden.

49:34.305 --> 49:35.639
That includes Lord INPYEONG…

49:38.100 --> 49:39.727
and most certainly, His Majesty.

49:48.486 --> 49:50.362
You are unwell,
so you should get some rest.

49:50.946 --> 49:53.741
I shall attend the engagement alone.

49:59.788 --> 50:01.456
I feel terrible.

50:01.457 --> 50:04.043
It appears I have upset
His Royal Highness.

50:05.085 --> 50:06.212
Do not be troubled.

50:07.880 --> 50:09.840
Hunting inherently requires

50:11.008 --> 50:12.676
patience above all.

50:34.031 --> 50:35.783
That woman by the Queen Mother's side.

50:36.450 --> 50:38.785
Conduct a comprehensive
background check on her.

50:38.786 --> 50:39.787
Yes, sir.

50:40.579 --> 50:41.580
No.

50:43.123 --> 50:44.457
Start with Jeongui Daily.

50:44.458 --> 50:45.875
Look into them first.

50:45.876 --> 50:47.336
Understood, sir.

50:51.632 --> 50:52.633
Your Royal Highness.

50:53.175 --> 50:55.343
You have a missed call from Ms. Seong.

50:55.344 --> 50:56.345
Several, actually.

51:09.316 --> 51:11.485
THREE MISSED CALLS
JUNIOR ALUM

51:22.538 --> 51:23.621
Your Royal Highness.

51:23.622 --> 51:25.457
What do you need? I'm busy.

51:25.958 --> 51:27.876
Uh, I'm also really…

51:33.674 --> 51:34.967
Let's not get angry.

51:35.551 --> 51:37.845
You must take pity on this poor soul.

51:41.515 --> 51:42.516
Your Royal Highness.

51:43.100 --> 51:45.477
I'm only going to say this once,
so listen carefully.

51:46.854 --> 51:48.022
I'm on your side.
:cue

51:52.985 --> 51:57.323
What I mean is, I can only succeed
if you succeed as well.

51:57.990 --> 52:00.701
Husband and wife stand as one, right?

52:01.452 --> 52:05.079
I'm not saying this
because I adore you or anything,

52:05.080 --> 52:06.373
so don't get too excited.

52:09.918 --> 52:11.128
Are you still there?

52:12.046 --> 52:13.172
Hello?

52:14.840 --> 52:15.883
Your Royal Highness?

52:17.635 --> 52:18.636
Did he hang up?

52:19.178 --> 52:20.220
Oh, he did.

52:21.930 --> 52:22.931
Cool.

52:28.354 --> 52:30.356
JUNIOR ALUM

52:43.160 --> 52:44.912
- Choi Hyeon.
- Yes, Your Royal Highness?

52:48.499 --> 52:50.124
I made sure to run over.

52:50.125 --> 52:51.585
Did someone ask you to?

52:52.753 --> 52:53.961
Pardon?

52:53.962 --> 52:55.756
I will head to my private residence
in the evening.

52:56.590 --> 53:00.010
Uh, but Prime Minister Min
requested you stay in the palace…

53:00.803 --> 53:04.932
But where did he come up
with such nonsense?

53:05.683 --> 53:07.267
I shall prepare accordingly.

53:20.406 --> 53:22.574
- To the internet café!
- Remember last time…

53:26.078 --> 53:27.621
Your Majesty!

53:28.622 --> 53:30.791
- Are you all right, Your Majesty?
- Yeah.

53:31.291 --> 53:32.835
Behave yourself before His Majesty!

53:33.544 --> 53:35.003
My apologies, Your Majesty.

53:42.594 --> 53:43.928
You should be more careful.

53:43.929 --> 53:46.014
Yes, Your Majesty. Please get back safely.

53:47.266 --> 53:48.475
- Hey.
- Wait for me.

53:49.685 --> 53:50.728
This way, Your Majesty.

53:56.900 --> 53:59.485
What are you doing here,
Prime Minister Min?

53:59.486 --> 54:02.197
Today is not Sunday.

54:03.699 --> 54:04.950
I am aware, Your Majesty.

54:05.451 --> 54:08.411
Unfortunately, I must deal
with an urgent matter this weekend.

54:08.412 --> 54:11.873
I am afraid I must cancel
this Sunday's history lesson.

54:11.874 --> 54:13.916
Official duties must take priority.

54:13.917 --> 54:14.918
Instead,

54:15.586 --> 54:16.837
we will have a lesson today.

54:17.671 --> 54:20.674
Or we could just skip it.

54:26.472 --> 54:27.514
Come this way!

54:37.983 --> 54:39.485
I wish I could play.

54:49.620 --> 54:50.662
Prime Minister Min.

54:51.872 --> 54:52.873
Yes, Your Majesty?

54:53.457 --> 54:55.209
I would like to make a request.

54:59.671 --> 55:03.758
One, two, three, four.

55:03.759 --> 55:06.928
Five, six, seven.

55:06.929 --> 55:08.930
We keep a smile on our face.

55:08.931 --> 55:11.307
Smile. With elegance.

55:11.308 --> 55:12.433
There you go.

55:12.434 --> 55:15.103
One, two, three…
Straighten your back!

55:17.105 --> 55:19.024
- Again!
- Again. Go.

55:19.566 --> 55:20.859
:cue

55:26.323 --> 55:30.827
We once again steady our breathing,
while maintaining a smile on our face.

55:31.328 --> 55:34.330
One, two, three, four.

55:34.331 --> 55:39.377
- Five, six, seven, eight.
- At this rate, she'll break all the china.

55:39.378 --> 55:41.838
I know, right? They're not cheap, either.

55:42.339 --> 55:44.508
But does that even help?

55:45.008 --> 55:46.842
I've seen it in period dramas before.

55:46.843 --> 55:49.053
- Put your arms down.
- I doubt it.

55:49.054 --> 55:50.389
Smile!

55:51.306 --> 55:52.515
Smile!

55:52.516 --> 55:54.226
There you go, with elegance.

55:55.018 --> 55:57.562
Six, seven, eight!

55:57.563 --> 56:00.773
One, two, three, four.

56:00.774 --> 56:03.818
Five, six, seven, eight.

56:03.819 --> 56:05.153
-  Your Majesty!
- There--

56:06.113 --> 56:07.155
Hello, Your Maje…

56:16.331 --> 56:17.416
So you're saying

56:18.041 --> 56:19.625
you basically played hooky?

56:19.626 --> 56:20.876
How dare you!

56:20.877 --> 56:23.589
I am here to see Uncle.

56:24.089 --> 56:25.799
Did you make an appointment?

56:27.384 --> 56:30.928
Well… No, I did not.

56:30.929 --> 56:32.388
Exactly.

56:32.389 --> 56:35.099
You showed up
without even making an appointment.

56:35.100 --> 56:36.602
To play with your uncle.

56:37.227 --> 56:38.770
That's what playing hooky is.

56:42.941 --> 56:43.942
Well done.

56:45.027 --> 56:46.402
You only live once.

56:46.403 --> 56:48.113
You should play hooky at least once.

56:49.156 --> 56:50.324
Shall we?

56:57.956 --> 56:59.124
What do you want to do?

57:00.000 --> 57:03.170
He has been a bit overwhelmed recently.

57:04.212 --> 57:05.839
He's still young.

57:07.132 --> 57:09.426
If only there were
an age limit for being king.

57:10.385 --> 57:11.386
It's too bad.

57:13.847 --> 57:15.307
Yes…

57:18.727 --> 57:19.728
Sorry.

57:20.228 --> 57:22.813
My husband just wouldn't let me go.

57:22.814 --> 57:26.359
Hmm. You two dated for years,
and you still like each other?

57:26.360 --> 57:28.819
Of course. I like him more every day.

57:28.820 --> 57:30.571
He gets more handsome every day.

57:30.572 --> 57:32.573
And he treats me
better and better every day.

57:34.576 --> 57:37.788
As you should.
You abandoned your family to marry him.

57:38.580 --> 57:39.623
What?

57:40.666 --> 57:44.794
I mean, everyone knows you made
your father collapse when you got married.

57:44.795 --> 57:47.923
He threatened to disown you
and ban you from using the Han name.

57:48.423 --> 57:49.507
It caused quite a stir.

57:49.508 --> 57:50.841
Stop that.

57:50.842 --> 57:53.094
Nobody talks like that anymore.

57:53.095 --> 57:54.470
Oh, please.

57:54.471 --> 57:57.890
Everyone still judges people by status
and pedigree behind closed doors.

57:57.891 --> 57:59.226
We're just jealous.

57:59.726 --> 58:02.395
People like us would never dream of
marrying for love.

58:04.356 --> 58:06.816
I guess you have no idea
what's happening in the world

58:06.817 --> 58:09.151
because you're always cooped up
in your chambers.

58:09.152 --> 58:11.862
My sister-in-law, with her lowly pedigree,

58:11.863 --> 58:13.824
is dating the Grand Prince.

58:14.449 --> 58:15.701
Haven't you heard?

58:22.499 --> 58:23.791
What's wrong?

58:23.792 --> 58:24.918
That witch!

58:25.794 --> 58:28.129
Kim Jaegyeong was like that in school too.

58:28.130 --> 58:29.797
She's just so nasty.

58:29.798 --> 58:32.467
Maybe I should've just dragged her
out of there by her hair.

58:33.343 --> 58:35.010
You should have.

58:35.011 --> 58:36.638
What? Can I do that?

58:37.597 --> 58:39.014
Why not?

58:39.015 --> 58:41.977
Make sure you grab it next time.
I'll cover the settlement.

58:43.270 --> 58:45.021
My sweet husband.

58:45.564 --> 58:48.691
Of course. Money comes before dignity.

58:48.692 --> 58:50.110
This is why you make money.
:cue

58:54.489 --> 58:57.075
Here I go.

58:57.576 --> 58:58.618
Done.

58:59.661 --> 59:00.746
Good.

59:01.538 --> 59:02.539
All right.

59:05.959 --> 59:07.002
Now…

59:09.713 --> 59:12.256
you get three chances to hit this pebble.

59:12.257 --> 59:13.966
One, two, three.

59:13.967 --> 59:15.926
If it lands inside this circle,

59:15.927 --> 59:17.803
all this land becomes Your Majesty's.

59:17.804 --> 59:19.556
- Easy, right?
- It is.

59:22.601 --> 59:23.602
Jeongwoo!

59:28.190 --> 59:30.817
Min Jeongwoo!

59:35.697 --> 59:36.906
Yes? What do you need?

59:36.907 --> 59:38.158
Jeongwoo…

59:40.118 --> 59:42.996
Prime Minister Min,
you will be the referee.

59:43.622 --> 59:44.705
Me?

59:44.706 --> 59:46.791
The loser has to grant the winner's wish.

59:46.792 --> 59:49.210
Rock, paper, scissors.

59:49.211 --> 59:50.378
I won.

59:51.129 --> 59:52.213
Here we go.

59:52.214 --> 59:53.548
That's one.

01:00:09.439 --> 01:00:11.065
Got you!

01:00:11.066 --> 01:00:12.483
- I got someone!
- My goodness!

01:00:17.364 --> 01:00:21.493
Green light… Red light.

01:00:22.160 --> 01:00:23.578
Youngseon, you moved.

01:00:24.079 --> 01:00:26.706
Green light…

01:00:30.210 --> 01:00:32.962
One, two, three.

01:00:32.963 --> 01:00:35.881
- Four, five, six, seven.
- Five, six, seven.

01:00:35.882 --> 01:00:37.174
- One, two.
- One, two.

01:00:37.175 --> 01:00:40.345
- Four!
- Four, five!

01:00:40.887 --> 01:00:42.054
One, two!

01:00:44.558 --> 01:00:45.892
Well done, Your Majesty!

01:00:58.154 --> 01:00:59.405
Wow!

01:00:59.406 --> 01:01:00.866
I won!

01:01:02.951 --> 01:01:04.953
I said I won!

01:01:11.751 --> 01:01:13.003
You did not forget, right?

01:01:14.754 --> 01:01:15.838
What?

01:01:15.839 --> 01:01:18.300
You promised to grant me a wish.

01:01:19.301 --> 01:01:20.302
I said that?

01:01:22.012 --> 01:01:24.639
Are you a man of virtue or of profit?

01:01:30.145 --> 01:01:31.229
I remember.

01:01:37.694 --> 01:01:39.446
This is your wish?

01:01:40.030 --> 01:01:41.448
I saw it when I arrived.

01:01:42.157 --> 01:01:44.576
I have always wanted
to ride one with the wings.

01:01:45.368 --> 01:01:46.827
You cannot, Your Majesty.

01:01:46.828 --> 01:01:49.413
It is not an approved vehicle.

01:01:49.414 --> 01:01:53.375
But it is a car with wings!

01:01:53.376 --> 01:01:57.212
It's the only one in the country!

01:01:57.213 --> 01:01:59.131
Observing protocol is a matter of customs.

01:01:59.132 --> 01:02:02.343
It is the duty of a man of virtue
to uphold propriety and decorum.

01:02:02.344 --> 01:02:03.678
Have you forgotten?

01:02:16.274 --> 01:02:19.611
Why are you all saying
I cannot do anything? Why?

01:02:20.403 --> 01:02:22.905
I am the king!

01:02:22.906 --> 01:02:25.991
- I should be able to do what I want!
- My goodness, Your Majesty.

01:02:25.992 --> 01:02:26.993
What did you just say?

01:02:27.702 --> 01:02:30.956
His Majesty is at your private residence
with Prime Minister Min.

01:02:32.165 --> 01:02:33.374
What's he doing there?

01:02:33.375 --> 01:02:35.794
How would I know?

01:02:38.088 --> 01:02:41.299
You will be back
before the palace gates are shut, right?

01:02:42.634 --> 01:02:45.720
Be sure to keep your eyes on the road.
Don't forget your seat belt.

01:02:47.597 --> 01:02:49.057
Call me later, sir!

01:02:54.312 --> 01:02:55.563
Hmm.

01:03:01.569 --> 01:03:03.988
You must keep
the windows closed at all times.

01:03:03.989 --> 01:03:06.116
Yes, I'll be sure to keep them closed.

01:03:08.952 --> 01:03:10.120
Must you be the driver?

01:03:12.288 --> 01:03:14.873
It's the only one in the country.

01:03:14.874 --> 01:03:18.169
I don't want anyone else driving it.
:cue

01:03:20.672 --> 01:03:23.841
I will be in the escort vehicle
ahead of you and clear the road.

01:03:23.842 --> 01:03:25.843
You must not go above 60 km per hour.

01:03:25.844 --> 01:03:27.929
And you must stay on the phone with me.

01:03:28.471 --> 01:03:29.681
If, by any chance,

01:03:30.557 --> 01:03:32.726
an unexpected situation arises…

01:03:33.309 --> 01:03:34.644
Don't worry.

01:03:35.228 --> 01:03:38.439
I will put His Majesty's safety
above all else.

01:03:45.864 --> 01:03:48.407
- And the rear security detail?
- Have them follow me.

01:03:48.408 --> 01:03:50.826
I will follow behind Ms. Seong's car.

01:03:50.827 --> 01:03:52.412
You will?

01:03:52.996 --> 01:03:56.790
If security details surround her car,
people will assume it's a motorcade.

01:03:56.791 --> 01:03:58.459
It might attract spectators.

01:03:58.460 --> 01:04:00.252
If they discover His Majesty inside--

01:04:00.253 --> 01:04:01.670
No, that cannot happen!

01:04:03.798 --> 01:04:05.382
May I borrow a car?

01:04:05.383 --> 01:04:06.801
Something discreet.

01:04:31.409 --> 01:04:32.701
Are there any issues?

01:04:32.702 --> 01:04:34.787
No, we're fine.

01:04:34.788 --> 01:04:36.955
We're going too slow. That's the issue.

01:04:36.956 --> 01:04:38.958
Can we not go any faster?

01:04:50.553 --> 01:04:53.306
Let's go!

01:04:57.811 --> 01:04:59.187
What's wrong with this?

01:05:07.028 --> 01:05:08.154
Your Majesty!

01:05:09.197 --> 01:05:10.198
Damn it.

01:05:16.913 --> 01:05:18.664
Your Majesty.

01:05:18.665 --> 01:05:20.625
You have your seat belt on, right?

01:05:35.056 --> 01:05:36.683
Seong Huiju, what's wrong?

01:05:37.767 --> 01:05:38.893
Jeongwoo!

01:05:39.477 --> 01:05:41.646
The brakes aren't working!

01:05:49.237 --> 01:05:51.239
Your Majesty, close your window.

01:06:43.499 --> 01:06:44.500
YANGSEO-GYO BRIDGE

01:07:08.900 --> 01:07:10.693
Hang on tight, Your Majesty.

01:07:11.819 --> 01:07:12.862
:cue

01:09:03.765 --> 01:09:06.684
PERFECT CROWN

01:09:43.304 --> 01:09:44.846
You even hurt your face?

01:09:44.847 --> 01:09:46.723
When that's all you have going for you?

01:09:46.724 --> 01:09:48.267
Someone messed with your car.

01:09:48.935 --> 01:09:50.060
Let's reconsider this.

01:09:50.061 --> 01:09:51.311
This marriage.

01:09:51.312 --> 01:09:54.482
There has been nothing but trouble
since Prince I-AN entered your life.

01:09:55.066 --> 01:09:56.359
Let's call off this marriage.

01:09:59.362 --> 01:10:00.947
What the hell are you doing?

01:10:01.531 --> 01:10:02.949
This is how you protect someone.

